{"tid":893872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【無線新聞唔會報道】福建洩7噸「毒碳九」，中國政府隱瞞，重創漁港多人送院","createTime":"2018-11-08T03:36:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-08T06:41:45.000Z","uid":202464,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8477f431972f499f86adf00e511811caf8521ba6","tid":893872,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T03:36:23.000Z","msg":"福建東港石油化工公司的船隻，周日（4日）在泉州市泉港區碼頭進行裝卸操作時，因軟管墊片老化、破損，導致近7噸化工原料「碳九」洩漏。有傳，已有村民因接觸洩漏物後身體不適入院，甚至有人因掉入污染海域被送進醫院ICU，當地漁排損失嚴重。有指，「碳九」組成份子複雜，沒法分解，同時易於吸入人體，比毒藥還毒。當局事後卻企圖掩飾事件"},{"pid":"e04dbe6f298932295b78091ff1df72d684184e28","tid":893872,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T04:38:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0001974cb4cf581347e3ac23bdcaf59acbf72926","tid":893872,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T06:26:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b292510ce22bd0b70fc76d9d197c60d878eb4219","tid":893872,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T06:41:45.000Z","msg":"有害氣體無害"}]}